---
description: AI, redaction, evaluation, and grounded-output rules
globs:
  - "apps/api/**/ai/**"
  - "apps/worker/**/ai/**"
  - "apps/api/**/privacy/**"
  - "apps/worker/**/privacy/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

External LLM input must be sanitized and policy-approved.

Use a provider-neutral interface and validated structured outputs.
Reject unknown issue codes and nonexistent evidence IDs.
Store prompt/rubric/model versions, input/output hashes, cost, latency, and validation status.
Never store chain-of-thought.
CRM outcomes are factual authority.
High-impact or low-confidence results require human review.
No cross-tenant training without explicit legal and contractual approval.
